{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gather Ingredients in Nature</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/extras/OP_1th_gif.gif?t=1669806972\" /><br>There are various resources in nature such as herbs, mushrooms, leaves and stones, and you can collect these resources by consuming energy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Craft Potions With the Ingredients You Collect</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/extras/OP_2th_gif.gif?t=1669806972\" /><br>Process the ingredients you collect, buy potion recipes from the bazaar and produce various potions by mixing ingredients into the cauldron according to the recipes you purchased.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use Potions</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/extras/3th_gif_OP.gif?t=1669806972\" /><br>You can use potions to regenerate yourself, you can use damage potions for hunting, and you can give workers special potions to make their work faster and more efficient.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sell Nonessential Ingredients and Potions in the Bazaar</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/extras/OP_4th_gif.gif?t=1669806972\" /><br>You can earn money and reputation by selling all the ingredients and potions you collect in the bazaar.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1669806972","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1669806972","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1669806972","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2018700/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1669806972","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":